#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/caching-settings-panel.html.php:2
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/caching-settings-panel.html.php:3
#: wp-google-maps-gold/includes/cache/class.cache.php:67
#
msgid "Cache Settings"
msgstr "Configuración de caché"

#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/caching-settings-panel.html.php:7
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/caching-settings-panel.html.php:8
#
msgid "Enable Caching (beta)"
msgstr "Activar caché (beta)"

#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/caching-settings-panel.html.php:20
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/caching-settings-panel.html.php:25
msgid "An experimental map caching system which will provide better loading times for large datasets. This is still in development, and may result in inconsistencies in some modules"
msgstr "Sistema experimental de caché de mapas para mejorar tiempos con datasets grandes. En desarrollo, puede causar incongruencias"

#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/caching-settings-panel.html.php:28
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/caching-settings-panel.html.php:33
#
msgid "Cached Data"
msgstr "Datos en caché"

#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/caching-settings-panel.html.php:46
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/caching-settings-panel.html.php:47
#
msgid "Beta Note:"
msgstr "Nota beta:"

#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/caching-settings-panel.html.php:47
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/caching-settings-panel.html.php:48
msgid "We currently only cache marker data, specifically focused on first load times. Shape data and marker listings are not cached in this build, but we expect this will change in the future"
msgstr "Actualmente solo cacheamos datos de marcadores, enfocado a tiempos de primera carga. Datos de formas y listados no están cacheados, cambiará en el futuro"

#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/caching-settings-panel.html.php:55
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/caching-settings-panel.html.php:55
#
msgid "Enable Deferred Caching"
msgstr "Activar caché diferida"

#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/caching-settings-panel.html.php:68
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/caching-settings-panel.html.php:72
msgid "This will load the cached data after the page loads, which can lead to better performance for very large datasets."
msgstr "Cargará los datos en caché tras la carga de la página, puede mejorar el rendimiento con datasets muy grandes."

#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:2
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:4
msgid "Live Tracking Settings"
msgstr "Configuración de Seguimiento en Directo"

#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:7
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:11
#
msgid "Enable Realtime Updates"
msgstr "Activar actualizaciones en tiempo real"

#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:20
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:29
msgid "Refresh maps at a set interval to allow users to watch location changes in realtime, on your website."
msgstr "Actualiza los mapas a intervalos definidos para que los usuarios vean cambios de ubicación en tiempo real."

#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:28
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:40
#
msgid "Refresh Interval"
msgstr "Intervalo de actualización"

#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:32
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:46
#
msgid "60 sec (Default)"
msgstr "60 seg (predeterminado)"

#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:33
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:47
msgid "45 sec"
msgstr "45 seg"

#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:34
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:48
msgid "30 sec"
msgstr "30 seg"

#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:35
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:49
msgid "20 sec"
msgstr "20 seg"

#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:36
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:50
msgid "15 sec"
msgstr "15 seg"

#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:37
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:51
msgid "10 sec"
msgstr "10 seg"

#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:38
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:52
msgid "5 sec"
msgstr "5 seg"

#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:45
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:57
msgid "Adjust how frequently you would like realtime updates to be refreshed, this will increase resource load on your server."
msgstr "Ajusta la frecuencia de actualización en tiempo real, aumentará la carga del servidor."

#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:47
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:59
msgid "Refresh intervals below 15 seconds will require a powerful server, as these frequencies tend to have a high impact on server load."
msgstr "Intervalos por debajo de 15 segundos requieren un servidor potente, estas frecuencias impactan mucho en la carga."

#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:52
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:67
msgid "Live Tracking Devices"
msgstr "Dispositivos de Seguimiento en Tiempo Real"

#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:59
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:75
msgid "Devices which have attempted to pair with your site will appear here. You must approve devices before they will appear on the map."
msgstr "Los dispositivos que han intentado emparejarse con su sitio aparecerán aquí. Debe aprobar los dispositivos para que aparezcan en el mapa."

#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:67
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/live-tracking-settings-panel.html.php:84
