msgstr "1 - 5: Tradicional \"de una a cinco\" estrellas"

#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/atlas-novus/marker-rating-settings.html.php:45
#: wp-google-maps-gold/html/marker-rating-settings.html.php:51
#: wp-google-maps-pro/html/marker-rating-settings.html.php:51
